This is an opinionated theme, used by pmario.

* Compact title bar: subtitle (modifier + relative modified date) sits inline to the right of the title and wraps below when the title is long
* Tiddler toolbar controls float to the top right of the title row
* Clicking a tag pill opens the Tiddler Info panel and selects the //Tag Map// tab directly

!! License

CC-BY-NC-SA - {{$:/themes/wikilabs/slant-01/license}}

